com.cognex.mobile.barcode.sdk

Class ReaderDevice

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cognex.mobile.barcode.sdk.ReaderDevice
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataManSystem.OnConnectedListener, DataManSystem.OnConnectionErrorListener, DataManSystem.OnDisconnectedListener

    public abstract class ReaderDevice
extends Object
implements DataManSystem.OnConnectedListener, DataManSystem.OnDisconnectedListener, DataManSystem.OnConnectionErrorListener
    Represents a Phone Camera or MX barcode reader You should instantiate this class using getPhoneCameraDevice() or getMXDevice() factory methods.
